* CMake
** http://cmake.org/cmake/help/v2.8.8/cmake.html
** add_subdirectory(/path) to execute another CMakeLists.txt
** exec_process( COMMAND make WORKING_DIRECTORY ${project_source_dir}/path/to/lib) (ex.: Makefile)
** exec_program(script.sh) to call a script
** cmake -LA: print all variables (do this from your build directory)
** Variables
*** http://www.cmake.org/Wiki/CMake_Useful_Variablesa
*** CMAKE_SOURCE_DIR
*** CMAKE_CURRENT_SOURCE_DIR
*** CMAKE_BINARY_DIR
*** CMAKE_CURRENT_BINARY_DIR
*** CMAKE_CURRENT_LIST_DIR
** https://stackoverflow.com/questions/4786861/cmake-link-external-c-library
** https://stackoverflow.com/questions/14306642/adding-multiple-executables-in-cmake
